    "type": "DecisionRecord",
    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-board",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team determined that the overall body of evidence is sufficient to accept the CFD hemolysis model for the VAD COU. The majority of assessed factors meet or approach required gradation levels, Monte Carlo UQ has been completed, and validation coverage spans four of five operating conditions. The two factors recorded without level data (Model form and Model inputs) are considered low-risk pending supplementary studies, and the team judged the remaining factor evidence collectively adequate to support acceptance.",
